2. cs.RO (Robotics) - The paper mentions the need for robots to build a model of the surrounding objects in order to operate autonomously, which is a common problem in robotics. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The paper proposes a deep neural network to generate images, which is a common technique in AI. 
4. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper uses a CNN-based object detector and a deep neural network, both of which are common machine learning techniques. 
5. cs.GR (Graphics) - The paper deals with generating images, which is a common problem in computer graphics.
